PrecisRegulations Amending the MIGRATORY BIRDS REGULATIONS by allowing the Minister to issue permits authorizing the holder to relocate nuisance birds in the manner described therein, and by clarifying the powers of the Minister with regard to the variation or suspension of the Regulations where urgent action is necessary for the conservation of migratory birds.
